{
  "stem": "25598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She either didn't have enough food or drink or what have you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyway, she wasn't producing milk, and the baby was very hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the baby was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the crying of the baby, under those circumstances, went on people's nerves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And people started to, to yell at her to shut up the baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And eventually she was under so much pressure that she took a brooch that she had on her coat and pricked her nipple to let the blood come, and she put the baby to her breast to suck the blood.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Things like this, which I dream about still today and which show me today-- I didn't understand it then-- how quickly that process of becoming inhuman happened.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Eventually, I think it was after three days and three nights, we arrived in a place called Ataki, which was in Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a border town-- used to be before the Germans and the Romanians invaded the Ukraine, it was a border town on the River Dniester.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And across this town was a larger city, called Mogilev, which was on the Russian side-- on Ukrainian territory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they-- the unloading of the train was also a very traumatic experience, because everything had to be done fast.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were shouting, and we were slipping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were full of manure and full of our own excrement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the-- and, and we ended up in this large field in the rain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I think there was some walking to do to this field, but I don't remember that part that well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "From the train to the field, I think there was some walking.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
